{"tid":1452722,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"喂！大撚鑊，我發現連登極多林鄭打手","createTime":"2019-08-12T02:11:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T06:54:31.000Z","uid":255970,"like":32,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"14d2c71d2a93514c61688dbc565df61b573617c9","tid":1452722,"uid":255970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T02:11:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0vzhTEL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0vzhTEL.png&h=e746f21b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n連登仔係咪<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">好鍾意林鄭？</span></span></strong>唔係嘅話就屌柒佢啦仆你個街！連登淡忘咗佢，佢依家開心到瞓唔着呀。<br />\n<br />\n警民關係破裂就唔使多講，文宣99%都屌緊黑警。<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">但成個連登冇人屌林鄭嘅喂？！</span></strong></span>乜料呀？<br />\n<br />\n林鄭係反送嘅始成俑者，依家呢個局面，佢有最大責任。流血、爆頭、爆眼、催淚彈，林鄭每一樣都有份！<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>每一筆血債都有佢個名！</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n唔好同我講冇人屌林鄭唔代表冇人嬲佢。實際上嘅情況係：如果我哋自自然然地唔講佢，就會令到大眾習慣咗冇林鄭，從而真真正正變咗「警民衝突」局面。<br />\n<br />\n大家要記得，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">主菜係林鄭同佢一班垃圾都不如、恬不知恥嘅問責狗官！</span></span></strong>警民衝突無錯係嚴重到不得了，但我哋喺屌柒黑警嘅同時，一定要將嗰條「警暴線」拉到去林鄭身邊，唔可以畀佢咁易就離開公眾嘅視視！<br />\n<br />\n連登開乜post都好，總會喺post末端寫上「光復香港」口號；同樣道理，開其他post時，都一定要拉林鄭落嚟！那怕係幾膠嘅句子都好。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥，血債血償！還返眼球畀救護姐姐！！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MnbwdDJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMnbwdDJ.png&h=da2a7041&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d47318e1df03485fc4d617048c00f573cd3de532","tid":1452722,"uid":255970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T02:13:00.000Z","msg":"自推pish"},{"pid":"2c150269462f368dc51aefaf7b3c98a35fd81e63","tid":1452722,"uid":255970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T02:13:16.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"1f11bf81fddb1dd6997c75803fe76584fba13e60","tid":1452722,"uid":144594,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T02:15:51.000Z","msg":"林鄭咪又係中共既一隻狗"},{"pid":"a33473f11641f36eb5d7043183519ad3754a9fa1","tid":1452722,"uid":77148,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T02:18:23.000Z","msg":"人人都係文宣組！文宣圖集中post<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1449111\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1449111</a>"},{"pid":"8e4cbe407c707635f62a816e6c90ca566d065863","tid":1452722,"uid":98431,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T02:21:49.000Z","msg":"ON9 起底"},{"pid":"f51640f010dc8bddba0bd1da908f5d39f9f6ebf7","tid":1452722,"uid":255970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1f11bf81fddb1dd6997c75803fe76584fba13e60","tid":1452722,"uid":144594,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T02:15:51.000Z","msg":"林鄭咪又係中共既一隻狗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T02:43:08.000Z","msg":"個個都知佢係隻狗，但都要搞（其實佢先係最撚仆街嗰個）<br />\n<br />\n大家屌到最尾，請喺文尾留返個位屌佢，唔該。"},{"pid":"8ddb527d3679498f5857216789829f528c2500f5","tid":1452722,"uid":255970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T02:43:38.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"a6a8272f40a779045e066698f856b76705c0373f","tid":1452722,"uid":290750,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T02:46:12.000Z","msg":"林奠死全家！绝子绝孫！"},{"pid":"fe2e1a45d92d5f7db7594d7234f823e4a2771bdf","tid":1452722,"uid":54381,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T02:46:26.000Z","msg":"林鄭一早已經唔係重點，係中共，而中共控制下嘅走狗係注定會成為目標"},{"pid":"9f96a283d80882ba49844ef7c72ad51efad61140","tid":1452722,"uid":54381,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fe2e1a45d92d5f7db7594d7234f823e4a2771bdf","tid":1452722,"uid":54381,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T02:46:26.000Z","msg":"林鄭一早已經唔係重點，係中共，而中共控制下嘅走狗係注定會成為目標"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T02:47:06.000Z","msg":"唔係唔洗清算林鄭，但係對個扯線公仔出火？"},{"pid":"30fa5ff6ce6857a95772e8407b4f1a5215b8fc50",